name: How to Understand the House Buying Process
summary:
Big breath: Tessa bought a flat. Stevie wants to know what it was like. If you or anyone you know are thinking of going through the flat (or house) buying process, this is the episode for you. Involves some WILD jargon, helpful hand-holding advice and something about paying for a war in the olden times which Stevie still canâ€™t get a handle on.
